document_data.name: Temple of Tymora
document_data.organizations: Organizations in the Temple of Tymora (Thruldar)
document_data.mainbody: The '''Temple of Tymora''' was a temple devoted to [[Tymora]], the Lady of Luck, located in the town of [[Thruldar]] in [[Estagund]] during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Description: The temple was one of the largest structures within Thuldar.
